        <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="Distinction from other species">
          <title>Distinction from other species.</title>
          <p>This new species can be distinguished from any other <italic><tp:taxon-name obkms_id="1ff7fed8-4868-4e9b-aa5c-0153d691842b" obkms_process="TRUE"><tp:taxon-name-part taxon-name-part-type="genus">Dorstenia</tp:taxon-name-part></tp:taxon-name></italic> species by its fernlike habit, hanging from vertical rock faces and the absence of latex.</p>
          <p>The new species is added to the existing key of <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B2">Berg and Hijman (1999)</xref> the “key to succulent and semi-succulent species of the Old World”</p>
